                Wanderlust Privacy Policy
            </h2>

            <p>At Wanderlust, we understand the importance of your privacy and are committed to safeguarding
                your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, disclose, and
                protect your information when you use our website or services. By accessing or using Wanderlust,
